# Koreny — Blazor WASM genealogy app

## Project
- Blazor WebAssembly standalone, .NET 10, no ASP.NET backend
- Static hosting: GitHub Pages (https://8khz.github.io/Koreny-PoC/)
- Repo: https://github.com/8khz/Koreny-PoC
- All data stays client-side — no API calls, no telemetry, no external services

## Dependencies
- GraphShape 1.2.1 + QuikGraph 2.5.0 — graph layout (may be removed after Dagre migration)
- Dagre v2.0.0 — loaded from CDN in index.html, used for FullGraph layout
- No other NuGet packages beyond Microsoft.AspNetCore.Components.WebAssembly
- No CSS frameworks
- xUnit for tests

## JavaScript
- All JS in wwwroot/js/dagre-layout.js — window.KorenyDagre.computeLayout
- All export functions inline in index.html as window.KorenyExport object
  (downloadText, downloadSvg, printSvg) — no dynamic module import
- No other JS files
- CDN scripts loaded in index.html before </body>:
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@dagrejs/dagre@2.0.0/dist/dagre.min.js"></script>
    <script src="js/dagre-layout.js"></script>

## Code style
- Nullable reference types enabled — treat all warnings as errors
- Implicit usings enabled
- @code blocks only — no code-behind (.razor.cs) files
- No comments on self-evident code — comments explain why, not what
- Constants for all magic numbers (dimensions, spacing, IDs)
- Idiomatic C#: records, init, pattern matching, expression bodies where natural

## Architecture
- AppState (singleton) — single source of truth for GedcomDocument
- GedcomParser: string → GedcomDocument (pure, stateless)
- GedcomWriter: GedcomDocument → string (pure, stateless)
- FamilyGraphLayoutService (singleton) — GraphShape layout, returns
  Dictionary<string, (double X, double Y)> — may be replaced by Dagre output
- Components are purely presentational — no direct AppState access,
  pass data via parameters and EventCallback

## Data model
- GedcomDocument: List<Individual>, List<Family>
- Individual: Id, GivenName, Surname, Sex (SexType), Birth, Death, Note,
  FamilyIds, RawTags (List<GedcomTag>) — round-trip preservation
- Family: Id, HusbandId, WifeId, ChildIds, Marriage, Note,
  RawTags (List<GedcomTag>) — round-trip preservation
- GedcomEvent: Date (string), Place, ParsedYear (int?)
- GedcomTag: Tag, Value, Children (List<GedcomTag>) — full GEDCOM tree
- GEDCOM IDs stripped of @ signs: @I001@ → "I001"

## Round-trip preservation (IN PROGRESS — parser broken)
- GedcomParser must build full GedcomTag tree for every INDI and FAM record
- GedcomWriter serializes RawTags tree — does not hardcode specific tags
- Goal: zero data loss when loading from MyHeritage/Ancestry and re-exporting
- Status: implementation attempted, parser currently broken — needs fix

## Visualization
- HourglassTree.razor: focus view, inline SVG, single click = re-root,
  double click = open edit form in right panel
- DescendantTree.razor: descendant overlay, SVG as <img> data URI
- FullGraph.razor: full family graph overlay, SVG as <img> data URI
  Layout via Dagre (JS interop) with virtual family nodes
  Virtual family node pattern: Individual nodes + Family dot nodes,
  edges: parent→FAMx→child, no direct husband→wife edge
  Orthogonal edge routing computed manually in C# from Dagre node positions
  Male: #4A7FB5, Female: #9B2335, Unknown: #888780, text white 13px

## Layout — Index.razor (single page)
Left panel (60%):
  Row 1: "Načíst GEDCOM" [hidden InputFile] | "Uložit GEDCOM"
  Row 2: "Celý strom" | "Celý graf"
  Row 3: "Osoby: N, rodiny: N" (when document loaded)
  <hr/>
  HourglassTree SVG visualization

Right panel (40%):
  Default state:
    "Nová osoba" | "Nová rodina"
    <hr/>
    "Upravit rodinu:" + family dropdown (format: "1. Jan N. + Marie S.") + "Otevřít"
    <hr/>
    Placeholder + scrollable individuals list (sorted by surname, given name)
  Edit state (person or family form open):
    All navigation hidden — edit form takes full panel
    Fields: given name, surname, sex, birth year/place, death year/place, note
    Buttons: "Uložit" | "Smazat" (hidden for new) | "Zrušit"

## Overlays
- DescendantTree: "Celý strom" button, closes via × or Escape
- FullGraph: "Celý graf" button, closes via × or Escape
- Both: solid white background, scrollable, SVG as <img> (native right-click save)
- FullGraph overlay toolbar: "Stáhnout SVG" | "Tisk" buttons

## GitHub Actions deploy
- dotnet publish -c Release → publish/wwwroot/Koreny-PoC/
- Fix fingerprinted blazor.webassembly.{hash}.js via sed
- publish_dir: publish/wwwroot/Koreny-PoC
- base href stays as "/" — StaticWebAssetBasePath handles subpath
- .nojekyll required

## Folder structure
Models/         — GedcomModels.cs only
Services/       — GedcomParser.cs, GedcomWriter.cs, AppState.cs,
                  FamilyGraphLayoutService.cs
Pages/          — Index.razor (only page)
Components/     — HourglassTree.razor, DescendantTree.razor,
                  FullGraph.razor, PersonBox.razor
wwwroot/js/     — dagre-layout.js
wwwroot/        — index.html (KorenyExport inline), favicon.svg, favicon.png

## Testing
- Koreny.Tests: xUnit, references main project
- GedcomParser: unit tests including round-trip test
- GedcomWriter: round-trip test (parse → write → parse → assert no data loss)

## Known issues
- GedcomParser round-trip preservation broken — needs fix after Dagre stabilization
- FullGraph edge routing being refined (Prompt 35 in progress)
- FamilyGraphLayoutService / GraphShape may be removable after Dagre fully works